      "date": "2013-10-06 23:48:41.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 3:\n\nbtw, this is correct place for patch. http://review.whamcloud.com/#/c/7864\n\nIt seems that this error happens when gcc is installed, but mpicc runs against Intel compiler. A quick workaround is replacing Intel compiler with gcc for mpicc, but something need to change environment. I will try adding a macro to keep original code, but skip it if other compiler is defined.",
